i pi pj bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"nz ik">Collabor=
ative Strategy Formulation:</strong> The system uses Ensemble Decision-Maki=
ng rather than a single agent. A =E2=80=9CBullish=E2=80=9D marketing agent,=
 a =E2=80=9CCautious Brand-Safety=E2=80=9D agent, and a =E2=80=9CData-Drive=
n ROI=E2=80=9D agent each propose campaign strategies. Their outputs are po=
sted to a shared Blackboard, where a =E2=80=9CCMO=E2=80=9D controller agent=
 synthesizes these perspectives into a coherent, robust plan.</li><li id=3D=
"2cef" class=3D"nx ny ij nz b jd pk ob oc jg pl oe of gf pm oh oi gi pn ok =
ol gl po on oo op si pi pj bg" data-selectable-paragraph=3D""><strong class=
=3D"nz ik">Long-Term Learning:</strong> Once a strategy is chosen, a =E2=80=
=9CJunior Copywriter=E2=80=9D agent iteratively drafts content using a Gene=
rate =E2=86=92 Critique =E2=86=92 Refine loop. Campaign performance, engage=
ment metrics, conversions is then fed back into a Self-Improvement Loop, cr=
eating a gold-standard dataset that improves the system=E2=80=99s performan=
ce for future tasks.</li><li id=3D"bfdc" class=3D"nx ny ij nz b jd pk ob oc=
 jg pl oe of gf pm oh oi gi pn ok ol gl po on oo op si pi pj bg" data-selec=
table-paragraph=3D""><strong class=3D"nz ik">Safe, Simulated Execution:</st=
rong> Final content undergoes a Dry-Run Harness for human approval of text =
and visuals. For higher-risk actions like ad-budget allocation, the agent r=
uns =E2=80=9Cwhat-if=E2=80=9D scenarios via a Simulator (Mental-Model-in-th=
e-Loop), predicting outcomes before any real-world commitment.</li></ol><bl=
ockquote class=3D"pp"><p id=3D"cbef" class=3D"pq pr ij bb ps pt tl tm tn to=
